HEADWORD: Philadelphia lawyer
<hw>Philadelphia lawyer</hw> <def>A lawyer knowledgeable about the most
detailed and minute points of law, especially one with an exceptional
propensity and ability to exploit fine technical points of law for the
client's advantage.</def> <mark>[U. S.]</mark> ⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Philadelphian</ent>⟦br⟧
